    "5_KZM_classes_not_generations": "Five KZM classes are graduated quench-rate levels, NOT 5 independent fermion families; all 5 correlate identically with diagonal-block T_munu. The fixed-ratio pattern sqrt(1, 1.5, 2, 3, 4) is structural but does not encode particle-physics generation labels.",
